text: Hirotaka Tamura is an electrical engineer at Fujitsu Laboratories Ltd. in Kawasaki, Japan. He was named a Fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) in 2013 for his contributions to technology for high speed interconnects. == References == Category:Fellow Members of the IEEE Category:Living people Category:Japanese engineers Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
